c11mux
======

c11mux is a modified work derived from cmux.

Original work
-------------
Name:     cmux
Author:   manaflow-ai
Source:   https://github.com/manaflow-ai/cmux
License:  GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 or later (AGPL-3.0-or-later)

Modifications
-------------
Modified by: Stage 11 Agentics
Fork date:   2026-04-16

Summary of modifications:
- Rebranded app identity (display name "c11mux", bundle ID "com.stage11.c11mux").
- New Homebrew tap (stage-11-agentics/c11mux) and release artifacts
  (c11mux-macos.dmg) published from the Stage 11 fork.
- Sparkle auto-update feed retargeted to Stage 11 releases.
- Diverged development after the fork point.

The CLI binary name, environment variables, socket protocol, shell
integration files, and source/module names remain identical to upstream
cmux for backward compatibility.

A complete, ongoing record of modifications is available in the git
history of the Stage 11 fork.

